[32m+[m[32m## Features[m
 [m
[31m-You can use any tools you like to help you complete the challenge. So if you've got something you'd like to practice, feel free to give it a go.[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Mobile-First Design:** The app is designed with a mobile-first approach for a seamless experience on various screen sizes.[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Add, Complete, and Delete Tasks:** Easily manage your to-do list.[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Drag and Drop:** Reorder tasks by dragging and dropping.[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Filter Options (All, Active, Completed):** Quickly toggle between different task views.[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Clear Completed:** Remove all completed tasks at once.[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Data Persistence:** Tasks are saved locally for return visits.[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Responsive:** Adapts to different screen sizes.[m
 [m
[31m-Your users should be able to:[m
[32m+[m[32m## Technologies Used[m
 [m
[31m-- View the optimal layout for the app depending on their device's screen size[m
[31m-- See hover states for all interactive elements on the page[m
[31m-- Add new todos to the list[m
[31m-- Mark todos as complete[m
[31m-- Delete todos from the list[m
[31m-- Filter by all/active/complete todos[m
[31m-- Clear all completed todos[m
[31m-- Toggle light and dark mode[m
[31m-- **Bonus**: Drag and drop to reorder items on the list[m
